      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="images/sample-1.jpg">
          <span class="card-title">Card Title</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <p>책 추천해주는 배너 넣는곳</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-action">
          <a href="#">This is a link</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

